  "bookTitle": "Ancient Demon Queen",
  "bookId": 40,
  "firstAcquaintance": "A legendary demon possessing world-shattering power. Right now, though, she's happily enjoying the New Year.",
  "personality": "Old-fashioned and traditional, she can be argumentative when confronted with new things she cannot easily accept. However, if treated with proper respect, she is willing to give them a chance.",
  "like": "Apples, tradition, minor mischief",
  "familiarData": "Primordial Lilith is Lilith's original personality, the very Serpent Demon Lilith recorded in historical texts - a great demon who has existed since the era of the first Demon Lord.\nFeeling that her past self was too unruly, she split off her chaotic personality. But she overcorrected, becoming relatively conservative and formal - the complete opposite of the current Lilith.\nThrough the power of the New Year, Primordial Lilith separated from the main body to act independently, possessing power no less formidable than when she once ruled the world. However, with the changing times and the festive atmosphere, she now simply wants to use her new body to experience the New Year of this era.\nWielding the primal power of magic, she can make her words become reality, easily placing curses on others. During the New Year, she combined this power with New Year's magic. Anyone who shows her disrespect is attacked with a battledore shuttlecock. If the shuttlecock strike lands, the victim receives an inescapable curse of having their face drawn on with ink - a rather... adorable punishment.",
